channel.title: I dl nd install jdk 6 nd 5.. but i just cant start my server
channel.description: So i install jdk 6 nd 5 just like anyone else correct.. i edit my Run thing to what yur supposed to ... but when i double click run to start my server.... it saids.. java.until.zip.ZipException: error in opening zip file... and then much more shit... PLEASE HELP im dieing to make a private server and i just cant ;( i am new at this so call me a noob.. but i just wanna learn.
